parameters:
\TA[1]Hey, the story is different, isn't it? You said that with
this power, you wouldn't give a damn about being a magical
girl!

\TA[1]In reality, the magical girls in this town were a piece of
cake, right?

\TA[1]After losing without even understanding their own
abilities, they resort to taking it out on others. It's
clear that they have hit rock bottom.
\TA[1]Shut up! All of you lost too, didn't you?
\TA[1]What the hell is that Invasoid bastard saying?

\TA[1]Listen up. That woman is mine. If you lay a hand on her
without permission, I'll knock you out.
\TA[1]She seems like she would be very helpful at my church.
\TA[1]Ahh!? I found them first, so where's the interruption?

\TA[1]And Invasoid, didn't I tell you that you can't
understand?!
\TA[1]We're not comrades or anything, anyway, right?

\TA[1]We just agreed not to interfere with each other's
information sharing.
\TA[1]If everyone desires it, the solution is simple.
\TA[1]The early bird gets the worm. Let's go with that.

\TA[1]It's easy to understand. It might be a little
disadvantageous for people who lack confidence.

\TA[1]Give me your power already. If I don't have priority, I'll
take what I can get.
\TA[1]Don't worry. I have plenty to keep me entertained over here.

\TA[1]Let's all do our best and completely mess up the magical
girls together ♡
